@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Auth API (.NET)" as Api
database "MySQL/MariaDB" as Db

== Register ==
User -> Client: submit email/password/display name
Client -> Api: POST /auth/register
Api -> Db: check email uniqueness
Db --> Api: not found
Api -> Api: hash password
Api -> Db: insert user + default role
Db --> Api: user id + role
Api -> Api: create JWT
Api --> Client: 201 Created + token

== Login ==
User -> Client: submit email/password
Client -> Api: POST /auth/login
Api -> Db: find user by email
Db --> Api: user + password hash + role
Api -> Api: verify password
Api -> Api: create JWT with role claim
Api --> Client: 200 OK + token
@enduml
